<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN"
            "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd">
<html metal:use-macro="options/maintemplate/macros/page">

  <div metal:fill-slot="body">

    <h1>PyX - Goals</h1>

    <p>
      The following table shows a list of planned enhancements to PyX. The
      planned features and their priority are subject to discussion on the
      <a href="http://sourceforge.net/mail/?group_id=45430">PyX mailing lists</a>.
      Note that completed items will be taken out of the list after they got
      documented and released.
    </p>

    <div class="tablepar">
      <table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=1>
        <tr><th class="tablehead">Goal</th><th class="tablehead">Status</th><th class="tablehead">Comment</th></tr>
        <tr><td colspan=3 class="tablehead">path system</td></tr>
        <tr><td>argument handling of multi-parameter path methods</td><td>need to be discussed</td><td>planned for one of the next releases</td></tr>
        <tr><td>MetaPost-like equation arithmetics</td><td>experimenal code</td><td>low priority</td></tr>
        <tr><td colspan=3 class="tablehead">boxes</td></tr>
        <tr><td>arbitrarily shaped boxes</td><td>experimental code</td><td>planned for one of the next releases</td></tr>
        <tr><td>clipping becomes a box property</td><td>not started</td><td>planned for one of the next releases</td></tr>
        <tr><td>union, intersection etc. of boxes</td><td>not started</td><td>low priority</td></tr>
        <tr><td colspan=3 class="tablehead">text</td></tr>
        <tr><td>improve TeX/LaTeX message handling (overful/underful boxes etc.)</td><td>not started</td><td>planned for 0.8 (wobsta)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>text in arbitrarily shaped boxes and float text from box to box</td><td>experimenal code</td><td>low priority</td></tr>
        <tr><td colspan=3 class="tablehead">graph system</td></tr>
        <tr><td>axis data handling</td><td>not started</td><td>planned for 0.8 (wobsta)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>merging of split and bar axes</td><td>not started</td><td>planned for 0.8 (wobsta)</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3d graph geometry and surface style</td><td>very old experimental code</td><td>planned for one of the next releases</td></tr>
        <tr><td>polar graph geometry</td><td>not started</td><td>planned for one of the next releases</td></tr>
        <tr><td colspan=3 class="tablehead">backend</td></tr>
        <tr><td>multi page support</td><td>experimental code</td><td>planned for one of the next releases</td></tr>
        <tr><td>pdf support</td><td>experimental code</td><td>planned for one of the next releases</td></tr>
        <tr><td>svg support</td><td>not started</td><td>low priority</td></tr>
        <tr><td>internal Type1 font stripping</td><td>not started</td><td>low priority</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

  </div>

</html>
